      • leftPad

        public static java.lang.String leftPad​(java.lang.String value,
                                       int length,
                                       char padChar)
        Left pad a string. Cube is a fixed width record format, so this helps with layout.
        Parameters:
        value - value being padded.
        length - total desired length.
        padChar - character to prepend to value to reach length.
        Returns:
        a String that is length characters long. NOTE: if value length is longer than length, value is truncated.
